Class FakeDataService

at.tuwien.vis2.metromaps.api.FakeDataService
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetroDataProvider
public class FakeDataService extends Object implements MetroDataProvider
This class is for testing with small datasets. Creates in memory lines and stations.
